Oakfield Studio Limited Privacy Policy
Oakfield Studio Limited respects your privacy rights and recognizes the importance of protecting any information collected about you. This Privacy Policy defines how we collect and use personal and non-personal information in our mobile applications and on our website.
BY INSTALLING, USING OR OTHERWISE ACCESSING OUR WEBSITE OR ANY MOBILE APPLICATION DEVELOPED OR PUBLISHED BY Oakfield Studio Limited, YOU AGREE TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY. IF YOU DO NOT AGREE TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY, PLEASE DO NOT INSTALL, USE OR OTHERWISE ACCESS OUR WEBSITE OR APPLICATIONS. We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at reasonable times, so please review it frequently. Your continued use of our applications will signify your acceptance of the changes to this Privacy Policy.
Personal Data:
Oakfield Studio Limited may allow you to register to receive updates on our products and services through our website.  The personal information we collect for this purpose is:
Name
E-mail Address
Personal information you submit on our website will not be used for this purpose unless you fill out the registration form.  We will not use the personal information you provide for any other purpose or share it with any 3rd-party without your explicit consent.
Non-Personal Data:
ADVERTISERS WHO SERVE ADS TO OUR MOBILE APPLICATIONS MAY USE TECHNOLOGY WHICH CAN UNIQUELY IDENTIFY MOBILE DEVICES TO DELIVER BETTER TARGETED MESSAGES AND CONTROL THE NUMBER OF TIMES YOU SEE A GIVEN AD.  AD NETWORKS MAY ACCESS YOUR UNIQUE DEVICE IDENTIFIER THROUGH THEIR OWN TECHNOLOGIES AND USE THIS IDENTIFIER TO TARGET ADVERTISING TO YOU BASED ON YOUR USE OF OUR APPLICATIONS AND OTHER ACTIONS YOU TAKE USING YOUR DEVICE.
Oakfield Studio Limited may use tools or third-party analytics software to collect and use certain non-personal data that does not enable us to identify you. The types of non-personal data we may collect and use include, but are not limited to: (i) unique mobile device identifier; (ii) mobile device type and device properties; (iii) mobile device software platform and firmware; (iv) mobile phone carrier; (v) game scores and achievements; and (vi) other non-personal data as reasonably required by Oakfield Studio Limited to enhance our services.
Oakfield Studio Limited may use the collected data for purposes of analyzing usage of our applications, managing and providing our applications, and to further develop our services and products. Oakfield Studio Limited reserves the right to use and disclose the collected non-personal data for purposes of advertisement by Oakfield Studio Limited or our partners.  Oakfield Studio Limited uses Flurry Analytics to analyze anonymous aggregated usage data for our applications.
Third Party Terms and Conditions:
Please note that your access to and the ability to play our applications may be subject to certain third party terms and conditions and privacy policies, including but not limited to application stores, mobile software platforms, on-line gaming platforms and payment providers. You recognize and agree that Oakfield Studio Limited is not liable for any such third party terms and conditions and their use of your personal data.
Links to Third Party Sites or Games:
Oakfield Studio Limited may at its discretion make available links through advertisements or otherwise enabling you to access third party sites or games. Please note that, while using such sites or games, you are using sites or games developed and administered by people or companies not affiliated with or controlled by Oakfield Studio Limited. Oakfield Studio Limited is not responsible for the actions of those people or companies, the content of their sites or games, the use of information you provide to them, or any products or services they may offer. Our link to those sites does not constitute our sponsorship of, or affiliation with, those people or companies.
